    <lb ed="T" n="0719b05"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0719b05"/><head><date from-iso="0689-12-21" key="j19730671978610" to-iso="0705-02-24">周</date><placeName key="PL000000023665">洛京魏國東寺</placeName><persName key="A001210">天智</persName>傳</head><p>
        <lb ed="T" n="0719b06"/><persName key="A001210">釋提雲般若</persName>，或云<persName key="A001210">提雲陀若那</persName>，華言<persName key="A001210">天智</persName>，
        <lb ed="T" n="0719b07"/><placeName key="PL000000047987">于闐國</placeName>人也。學通大小，解兼真俗<ptr target="#n344"/>，呪術禪
        <lb ed="T" n="0719b08"/>門，無不諳曉。<date from-iso="0689" key="j19727421973066" to-iso="0689"><anchor xml:id="beg0719002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>水</sic><corr>永</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0719002"/>昌</date>元年，來屆于此，謁<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>
<lb ed="T" n="0719b09"/>於<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，勅令就<placeName key="PL000000023665">魏國東寺</placeName>（後改<placeName key="PL000000023665">大周東寺</placeName>）翻譯。即
<lb ed="T" n="0719b10"/>以<date from-iso="0689" key="j19727421973774" to-iso="0691">其年己丑至天授二年辛卯</date>，出《華嚴經
        <lb ed="T" n="0719b11"/>法界無差別論》等六部七卷<ptr target="#n345"/>，沙門<persName key="A008996">處一</persName>筆受<ptr target="#n53"/>，
<lb ed="T" n="0719b12"/>沙門<persName key="A001192">復禮</persName>綴文，沙門<persName key="A002451">德感</persName>、<persName key="A008993">慧儼</persName>、<persName key="A008994">法明</persName>、<persName key="A008970">恒景</persName>等
        <lb ed="T" n="0719b13"/>證義<ptr target="#n54"/><ptr target="#n346"/>。<persName key="A001210">智</persName>終年卒地，莫得而聞。</p>
